Stop Service and take tar of current data directory:

[admin@crdb1 ~]$ sudo systemctl stop cockroachdb.service
Password:

[admin@crdb1 ~]$ su - cockroach
Password:
[cockroach@crdb1 ~]$ ls
certs  data
[cockroach@crdb1 ~]$ tar -czf data_node1.tar.gz data


